---
---

<section class="credibility">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Why me</h2>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="left">
        <p class="body">
          “Most Play Store submission-as-a-service freelancers haven’t actually been rejected by Google. I have — on my own apps. The Data Safety misalignment that killed stockportfolio.pro’s first submission, the policy gauntlet that suspended an earlier app — those weren’t theory. I learned the system by losing to it twice and winning five times.”
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="stats">
        <div class="row">
          <span class="num mono">5</span>
          <span class="label">Apps shipped to Google Play</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="num mono">2</span>
          <span class="label">Currently in Production</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="num mono">1</span>
          <span class="label">Rejection navigated</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="num mono">1</span>
          <span class="label">Suspension recovered</span>
        </div>
        <p class="note">Play Console screenshot available on request</p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .credibility {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding-block: 96px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 24px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-align: left;
    margin: 0 0 48px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
    }
  }

  .body {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .stats {
    background: var(--soft);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-block: 14px;
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--line);
  }

  .row:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1;
    min-width: 56px;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .note {
    margin: 16px 0 0 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
